events.title: GBM #3: Engineering Ethics
events.description:
Wed. (3/1), Cymer Conference Center @ 6PM (Check-in at 5:45PM)
Dr. Steve Starrett from Kansas State University and Dr. Carlos Bertha, a philosophy professor at the US Air Force Academy, will deliver a presentation about the importance on engineering ethics and how it plays a role in our profession.
